WEBVTT

00:00.583 --> 00:01.631
By the Book

00:02.548 --> 00:06.919
It means to do something exactly as the rules tell you.

00:08.221 --> 00:16.142
Companies today should do all business by the book to avoid problems with regulatory agencies and audits.

00:17.701 --> 00:24.485
While some chefs prefer to try unique ways to make food, others prefer to cook meals by the book.

